## Monorepo Scope Discipline

**CRITICAL**: Always identify which package(s) are affected and run checks in the correct scope.

### Webapp Libraries (packages/webapp-libs/)

| Package | Lint | Type-check | Test |
|---------|------|------------|------|
| `webapp-core` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-api-client` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-contentful` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-crud-demo` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-documents` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-notifications` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-emails` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-finances` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-generative-ai` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `webapp-tenants` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |

### Running Multiple Package Checks

```bash
# Run checks on multiple affected packages
pnpm nx run-many --target=lint --projects=webapp,webapp-core,webapp-tenants
pnpm nx run-many --target=type-check --projects=webapp,webapp-core,webapp-tenants
pnpm nx run-many --target=test --projects=webapp,webapp-core,webapp-tenants -- --watchAll=false
```

